==English==

===Noun Phrase===
'''victimless [[crime]]'''

#An act or behavior which is [[prohibit]]ed by [[law]], yet which neither directly harms nor violates the [[right]]s of any specific person, although some people may claim it harms [[society]] as a whole. This concept typically applies to [[adult]]s.

